)

См. определение в файле p_replay.cpp строка 57

58 {
59 // OSReport( "READ: 0x%08x - %d bytes\n", bufferOffset, numBytes );
60  Dbg_MsgAssert(sp_buffer,("Replay buffer has not been allocated"));
61  Dbg_MsgAssert(p_dest,("NULL p_dest sent to Replay::Read()"));
62  Dbg_MsgAssert(bufferOffset>=0 && bufferOffset<REPLAY_BUFFER_SIZE,("Bad bufferOffset of %d sent to Read()",bufferOffset));
63  Dbg_MsgAssert(bufferOffset+numBytes<=REPLAY_BUFFER_SIZE,("Requested Read() goes past the end of the buffer:\nbufferOffset=%d numBytes=%d REPLAY_BUFFER_SIZE=%d",bufferOffset,numBytes,REPLAY_BUFFER_SIZE));
64 
65 // memcpy(p_dest,sp_buffer+bufferOffset,numBytes);
66 
67  char buffer[MAX_BUFFER] __attribute__ (( aligned( 32 )));
68  int aligned_off = bufferOffset & 0xffffffe0;
69  int aligned_size = ( ( ( bufferOffset + numBytes ) - aligned_off ) + 31 ) & 0xffffffe0;
70 
71  if ( aligned_size > MAX_BUFFER )
72  {
73  OSReport( "Transfer too large: %d - max = %d\n", aligned_size, MAX_BUFFER );
74  while (1 == 1);
75  }
76 
77  NsDMA::toMRAM( buffer, sp_buffer+aligned_off, aligned_size );
78  memcpy( p_dest, &buffer[bufferOffset-aligned_off], numBytes );

◆ WriteIntoBuffer()

void Replay::WriteIntoBuffer ( uint8 *  p_source,
int  bufferOffset,
int  numBytes 
)
inline

См. определение в файле p_replay.cpp строка 82

83 {
84 // OSReport( "WRITE: 0x%08x - %d bytes\n", bufferOffset, numBytes );
85 
86  Dbg_MsgAssert(sp_buffer,("Replay buffer has not been allocated"));
87  Dbg_MsgAssert(p_source,("NULL p_source sent to Replay::Write()"));
88  Dbg_MsgAssert(bufferOffset>=0 && bufferOffset<REPLAY_BUFFER_SIZE,("Bad bufferOffset of %d sent to Write()",bufferOffset));
89  Dbg_MsgAssert(bufferOffset+numBytes<=REPLAY_BUFFER_SIZE,("Requested Write() goes past the end of the buffer:\nbufferOffset=%d numBytes=%d REPLAY_BUFFER_SIZE=%d",bufferOffset,numBytes,REPLAY_BUFFER_SIZE));
90 
91 // memcpy(sp_buffer+bufferOffset,p_source,numBytes);
92 
93  // First, we read what's in ARAM to MRAM, then copy our data in and DMA it back.
94  char buffer[MAX_BUFFER] __attribute__ (( aligned( 32 )));
95  int aligned_off = bufferOffset & 0xffffffe0;
96  int aligned_size = ( ( ( bufferOffset + numBytes ) - aligned_off ) + 31 ) & 0xffffffe0;
97 
98  if ( aligned_size > MAX_BUFFER )
99  {
100  OSReport( "Transfer too large: %d - max = %d\n", aligned_size, MAX_BUFFER );
101  while (1 == 1);
102  }
103 
104  NsDMA::toMRAM( buffer, sp_buffer+aligned_off, aligned_size );
105  memcpy( &buffer[bufferOffset-aligned_off], p_source, numBytes );
106  NsDMA::toARAM( sp_buffer+aligned_off, buffer, aligned_size );
